statements.sql:
SELECT `comment`.`data`,
`comment`.content,
`comment`.grade,
`comment`.bid,
`comment`.uid,
business.id,
business.`name`,
dealer.id
FROM `comment`, business, dealer
WHERE `comment`.bid = business.id AND business.did = dealer.id AND dealer.id = 1
